items.body_excerpt:
Source confirms the Hawks are signing Jalen Wilson to a Two-Way contract.

@mikeascotto.bsky.social had it first.

Wilson is a 25-year-old combo forward out of Kansas with a ton of NBA experience (176 games with Brooklyn) by Two-Way standards.

The No Offseason podcast that came out today featuring 
@zenakeita.bsky.social, @anniecostabile.bsky.social
and @sabreenajm.bsky.social really did a phenomenal job  discussing Sandy Brondello and Angel Reese. It was a conversation that included a ton of nuance and thought.
